stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> PaidInDb : checkout / webhook\nafter successful payment

    PaidInDb --> Dispensing : state = DISPENSING
    PaidInDb --> Completed : state = DONE\n(อาจข้าม DISPENSING ได้ตามลำดับ event)
    PaidInDb --> DispenseFailed : state = ERROR

    Dispensing --> Completed : state = DONE
    Dispensing --> DispenseFailed : state = ERROR

    DispenseFailed --> Refunded : background _auto_refund\n(Omise refund OK)
    DispenseFailed --> DispenseFailed : refund ล้มเหลว\nคง dispense_failed

    Completed --> [*]
    Refunded --> [*]
